SRP (US base price): Approx. $33,790+ (Price varies by trim, cab, and bed configuration)
SPECS:
Overall Dimensions: 213.0 in (length) × 76.9 in (width) × 74.0 in (height, varies by trim) Wheelbase: 131.9 in Seating Capacity: 5
ENGINE / PERFORMANCE
Engine (standard): 2.4 L turbocharged inline-4
Horsepower: 228 hp
Torque: 243 lb-ft
Engine (higher-output / optional for upper trims): 2.4 L turbocharged inline-4
Horsepower: 278 hp
Torque: 317 lb-ft
Transmission: 8-speed automatic Drivetrain: 2WD standard, part-time 4WD optional
CAPACITY & CAPABILITIES
Fuel Tank Capacity: 18.2 gallons
Maximum Towing Capacity: ~6,500 lbs (trim-dependent)
Maximum Payload Capacity: ~1,230–1,700 lbs (trim and bed-dependent)
INTERIOR / CABIN / SPACE
Front Headroom: ~39.7 in
Front Legroom: ~41.8 in
Rear Headroom: ~38.4 in
Rear Legroom: ~33.7 in (Double Cab)
CHASSIS / BRAKES / WHEELS / SUSPENSION
Suspension: Independent front; multi-link coil-spring rear
Brakes: 4-wheel disc brakes
Bed / Body Configurations: 5-ft or 6-ft bed depending on cab/trim
Wheels / Tires: 16–18 in alloy wheels depending on trim
